---
description: Pabbly and WhatsApp integration safety
globs: ["**/*message*", "**/*whatsapp*", "**/*pabbly*", "services/**/integrations/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Pabbly is a communication provider, not the patient or financial source of truth.
- Verify and deduplicate provider webhooks.
- Respect channel and purpose consent.
- Never send development messages to patients.
- Use only the owner and specifically approved staff test numbers.
- Do not connect the live number until the user approves a ready test workflow.
- Provider downtime must not block clinical work.
